      <title>投资者押注法国资产在大选后将面临数月波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/french-election-turmoil-to-have-prolonged-impact-on-stock-and-bond-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无论哪个政党在周日的法国议会选举中获胜，一些投资者都押注，这次选举将标志着该国股票和债券市场进入一个更加动荡的时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/french-election-turmoil-to-have-prolonged-impact-on-stock-and-bond-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国金融家聘请 Lazard 为失败的赞比亚交易提供咨询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-financier-hires-lazard-to-advise-on-zambia-deal-that-soured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国国际投资有限公司 (British International Investment Plc) 已聘请 Lazard Inc. 为其对赞比亚肉类生产商的可转换优先股投资提供建议，此前该公司的价值已缩水逾三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-financier-hires-lazard-to-advise-on-zambia-deal-that-soured</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房价有望从 2022 年的低迷中恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/swedish-housing-prices-on-track-to-recover-from-2022-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通胀冲击导致借贷成本上升，并导致房屋建筑几乎陷入停滞，瑞典房价已收回通胀冲击第一年所蒙受损失的近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/swedish-housing-prices-on-track-to-recover-from-2022-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧持续，铁矿石价格从一个月高位回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/iron-ore-slumps-from-one-month-high-as-demand-concerns-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者衡量中国需求复苏是否可持续，铁矿石价格从一个月高点回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/iron-ore-slumps-from-one-month-high-as-demand-concerns-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管股市创下历史新高，比特币仍跌至 2 月以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币连续第四个交易日下跌，这是加密货币更大范围抛售的一部分，与近期全球股市创下的历史新高形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行准备通过各大银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行采取了进一步措施，通过出售国债来冷却创纪录的股市上涨，并表示，目前通过与贷款机构达成的协议，央行可以持有“数千亿元”人民币的国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大批准嘉能可煤炭交易，泰克计划回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大已批准嘉能可公司（Glencore Plc）以 69 亿美元收购泰克资源有限公司（Teck Resources Ltd.）的冶金煤业务，后者宣布回购 20 亿美元股票并承诺提高铜产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风风险和美国库存下降导致油价接近两个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风贝丽尔预示着风暴季节可能会更加糟糕，而美国原油库存减少暗示需求增加，油价交易价格接近两个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
