      <title>全球股市创下新高，中国人民银行将借入债券：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员将注意力转向周五至关重要的美国就业数据，全球股市正在创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</guid>
