    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党获胜，股指期货上涨，英镑持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党赢得议会多数席位后，英国股指期货上涨，英镑维持近期涨势，这赋予了其履行更大经济稳定承诺的明确权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
